   <text lang="en">On October 24th 1944 near the Philippine islands of Leyte Japanese Combined Fleet launched aerial attack agaings ships of US Task Force 58. American F6F Hellcats stood up against this attack. Defend the fleet and shoot down all incoming bombers.</text>
